room_title: Escape room "Sector X" by Will to Escape in West Palm Beach
room_description:
â€‹Life was discovered on other planets and a secret mission has been formed to study new life across the universe.  The program chose you and your team as the science crew!

You are assigned to the research lab aboard the Orion Space Station and have been collecting specimens from all over the universe in hopes of understanding the far reaches of the galaxy. In a turn of events, a malfunction occurred in the containment chamber and a new species of alien life has escaped!!! Your mission is to locate the escaped specimen before it reproduces and takes over the entire ship!!!  You have one hour to restore the containment chamber, capture the alien and save the entire crew! 

Good luck space traveler...Godspeed!
